            Set up items with inventory numbers in your preferred format.
            Add elements, edit them, drag to reorder, or drag outside to delete.
        </p>

        <div class="mb-3">
            <strong>Example: </strong>
            <code id="customIdPreview" class="fs-5">Loading...</code>
